{"tid":1690283,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"請罷食深水步藍店 - 漢發麵店","createTime":"2019-11-03T08:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T19:04:46.000Z","uid":34047,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"27c20f2eeceb5f32a765d1f1e05437ff474823e2","tid":1690283,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z85UaY6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ85UaY6.jpg&h=dbed6977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9iyrxs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9iyrxs.jpg&h=0ac10f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源Phy li <br />\n<br />\n喺香港人的飲食購物天地見到！唔FC啦，因為絕對相信牙叻條仆街會咁講野！<br />\n<br />\n佢笑到眼突突咁撚様，相信間藍舖真係招呼得佢好舒服。<br />\n<br />\n一間招呼仆街招呼得咁開心嘅舖頭擺食係基本🤡<br />\n<br />\n挑拿星，間舖又話唔招呼出口傷人，無品，樣衰(呢個我加嘅，相信全香港無人反對)嘅食客嘅？依家大大碌楝係你面前，仲唔趕9佢走？<br />\n<br />\n#新資訊<br />\n<br />\n#藍 #深水涉<br />\n<br />\n#漢發麵家<br />\n<br />\n藍原因：老闆娘見到熟客荷蘭叻即刻比位佢，態度殷勤，荷蘭叻係店到大聲講今日出面好多曱甴，極之不屑！<br />\n枉個鋪面貼住出口傷人，冇品客人恕不招待！口出狂言嘅人個老闆娘仲笑晒咁同佢吹水，仲遞埋茶！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/802472909813345/posts/2650865854974032/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F802472909813345%2Fposts%2F2650865854974032%2F&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f91a18cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/802472909813345/posts/2650865854974032/</a>"},{"pid":"258785ea3d841c876f2419c96908093f3d88f4cf","tid":1690283,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e71c09c347dc54741d58b226ac386b15d8dcb0ee","tid":1690283,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"991620f25f99352445392707efff1873a0a9a177","tid":1690283,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"甴近平<br />\n習近平<br /